## Naming convention for the doc

`changes/<short-kebab-slug>.md` — short, kebab-case, descriptive of the work itself (not of the ticket number).

| Good | Bad |
|---|---|
| `account-trigger-recursion-fix.md` | `fix1.md` |
| `add-bulk-import-omniscript.md` | `STORY-12345.md` |
| `hfn-creation-async-batch-migration.md` | `refactor.md` |
| `practitioner-creation-flow-issues.md` | `JIRA-fix.md` |

A ticket reference belongs **inside** the doc (in the header block or §3 Requirements), not in the filename. Filenames must read well a year from now without the ticket tracker open.

