## Self-application

This ruleset itself was added in a single code commit — no `changes/` doc was written for it (avoiding chicken-and-egg recursion when the rule didn't yet exist). Every subsequent piece of Salesforce work in this repo (and any repo that adopts this rule) MUST follow the rule.
